----

We want our web to be accessible for everybody and from anywhere, no matter if you are using a computer or a mobile device.

The liquid design of our website lets you resize the browser's window (or display any webpage from different devices with different window sizes) keeping always the best look possible.

(Screenshots here...)

We also try not to use JavaScript except for side contents or functionalities.

Our website is fully compatible with the latest versions of the browsers listed bellow:

<ul><li>Firefox</li><li>Google Chrome or Chromium</li><li>Opera</li><li>Safari</li><li>Konqueror</li></ul>

?? If you are a Windows user and you are using Internet Explorer, we recommend you to use a faster browser adapted to the international web standards. You may want to download and install any of the following browsers (free of charge): <a href="http://www.mozilla-europe.org/firefox/" title="Download Firefox for Windows">Firefox</a>, <a href="http://www.google.com/chrome/" title="Download Google Chrome for Windows">Google Chrome</a>, <a href="http://www.opera.com/download/" title="Download Opera for Windows">Opera</a>, <a href="http://www.apple.com/safari/download/" title="Download Safari for Windows">Safari</a>.

Although not fully compatible, you can easily browse and access all contents in this website using almost any web browser.
